meta:
  origin:
    producer: Wang and Caminada
    title: Income inequality and fiscal redistribution in 47 LIS-countries, 1967-2014
    description: |-
      Gini data available at roughly five year intervals. Gini averaged for each country over the time period available. Time periods are: 1981-2010 for Australia, 1987-2013 for Austria, 1985-2000 for Belgium, 1971-2010 for Canada, 1987-2013 for Denmark, 1987-2013 for Finland, 1978-2010 for France, 1973-2013 for Germany, 1986-2014 for Italy, 1985-2013 for Luxembourg, 1983-2013 for Netherlands, 1979-2013 for Norway, 1967-2005 for Sweden, 1982-2013 for Switzerland, 1969-2013 for the United Kingdom and 1974-2013 for the United States.
    citation_full: 'Koen Caminada, Jinxian Wang, Kees Goudswaard & Chen Wang (2017), Income inequality and fiscal redistribution in 47 LIS-countries (1967-2014), LIS Working Paper Series No. 724.'
    url_main: https://www.universiteitleiden.nl/en/law/institute-for-tax-law-and-economics/economics/data-sets/leiden-lis-budget-incidence-fiscal-redistribution-dataset-on-income-inequality-for-47-lis-countries---1967-2014
    date_accessed: '2019-07-10'
    date_published: '2017'
  is_public: false
